T02D2763:140a-0: @140a * // 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs rtag pa'i rnal 'byor la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2763:140a-2: spyi gtsug cod pan rtag tu 'dzin //
T02D2763:140b-0: zhes @140b 'byung ba'i sgrub thams bshad par bya'o //
T02D2763:140b-2: rtsa lag gcig pu la btud de //
T02D2763:140b-3: de snying cod pan gtsug tor gyi //
T02D2763:140b-4: rnal 'byor cho ga bdag gis bshad //
T02D2763:140b-5: dben pa'i gnas 'dug 'khor ba'i me 'obs 'bar ba dang //
T02D2763:140b-6: bde ba'i rkyen tshogs yid skyo mngon dga' drag po yis //
T02D2763:140b-7: thar pa'i grong khyer rdul bral skyed mos tshal bzangs su //
T02D2763:140b-8: zhugs nas rjes 'jug dang ba dam pas sems dul bya //
T02D2763:140b-10: blo ldan rgyud rab brlan gyur pa //
T02D2763:140b-11: de nyid rjes thogs dpal gsum gyi //
T02D2763:140b-12: cho ga dam pa bsgom par bya //
T02D2763:140b-13: ae ma'o spyi gtsug rin chen khang //
T02D2763:140b-14: bkra shis mchod rten dri ma med //
T02D2763:140b-15: thub pa stong gis spras pa'i sgo //
T02D2763:140b-16: mgon po nyid kyis dbus mdzes pa'o //
T02D2763:140b-18: aa stong de dbus sems yig h'um //
T02D2763:140b-20: bum pa'i mar me 'bar ba bzhin //
T02D2763:140b-21: de bzhin lte ba'i dkyil 'khor dbus //
T02D2763:140b-22: nyi ma'am zla ba la gnas pa'i //
T02D2763:140b-23: rlung gi rgyal po me yi dbus //
T02D2763:140b-24: bde ba'i chus brlan mkhregs pa'i sa //
T02D2763:140b-25: rnam dag rnam par 'phrul pa'i rgyud //
T02D2763:140b-26: 'byung bzhi'i rang bzhin ram yig bsam //
T02D2763:140b-28: rtsa mchog 'dis brgyud skyob pa yis //
T02D2763:140b-29: thugs reg thugs bskul thugs byung ba'i //
T02D2763:140b-30: byin brlabs zhi byed dag byed dang //
T02D2763:140b-32: rnam bzhi bdud rtsi'i rgyun dbab bya //
T02D2763:140b-33: gang tshe ye shes mchog 'di babs gyur pa //
T02D2763:140b-34: de tshe mi g-yo 'od gsal rnam par dag / kun 'byung mtsho chen nyi 'dod sgron mchog dang //
T02D2763:140b-35: nam mkha'i yid bzhin nor bu ji bzhin no //
T02D2763:140b-36: bde chen gnyis su med nyed la //
T02D2763:140b-37: ji srid bzod par nus re srid //
T02D2763:140b-38: mnyam par gzhag bya mi gnas na //
T02D2763:140b-39: de tshe dge tshogs dpag med bsgrub //
